        "summary": "The Ministry of Steel will conduct an Open House to discuss issues related to import of steel on 9th of this month in New Delhi. The Ministry said that companies and associations can present their issues related to import of steel on this day. &#160; The Open House will be conducted from 11:00 AM to […]",
        "article": "The Ministry of Steel will conduct an Open House to discuss issues related to import of steel on 9th of this month in New Delhi. The Ministry said that companies and associations can present their issues related to import of steel on this day. &nbsp; The Open House will be conducted from 11:00 AM to 5:00 PM and specific time slots will be given through e-mail to the companies and associations. The Ministry said that walk-ins will not be possible due to logistical challenges and only one representative per organisation is permitted to ensure wider participation.",
